Detailed Description

A GfxTrafficInfoFeature.

Represents traffic information (such as an accident, road work etc.)

byte GfxTrafficInfoFeature::m_angle [private]
 

The angle of the traffic info.

Represented as parts of 255 in degrees, ie. angle_degree = m_angle / 255. Counted clockwise from north.
